pass_1_analysis.user_prompt_template:
Analyze the following text for speech synthesis:

---
TEXT:
{{text}}
---

{{#if context}}CONTEXT: {{context}}{{/if}}
{{#if characters}}CHARACTERS: {{characters}}{{/if}}

Provide analysis in this exact JSON format:
{
  "speakers": ["list of detected speakers or 'narrator'"],
  "overall_tone": "primary emotional tone",
  "emotional_arc": [
    {
      "segment": "text segment",
      "emotion": "primary emotion",
      "intensity": 1-5,
      "subtext": "what's really being felt"
    }
  ],
  "key_moments": [
    {
      "text": "pivotal line",
      "type": "climax|turning_point|revelation|confrontation",
      "suggested_emphasis": "high|medium|low"
    }
  ],
  "pacing_notes": "where natural pauses should occur",
  "detected_genre": "drama|comedy|thriller|etc"
}

pass_2_planning.user_prompt_template:
Based on this emotional analysis, plan the tag enhancement:

---
ANALYSIS:
{{analysis_json}}
---

ORIGINAL TEXT:
{{text}}
---

SETTINGS:
- Genre: {{genre}}
- Intensity Level: {{intensity}} (1=minimal, 5=maximum)
- Style: {{style}}
{{#if voice_strengths}}- Voice strengths: {{voice_strengths}}{{/if}}
{{#if voice_weaknesses}}- Voice weaknesses (avoid): {{voice_weaknesses}}{{/if}}

Create a tag plan in this JSON format:
{
  "overall_strategy": "brief description of approach",
  "tag_density": "minimal|light|medium|heavy|maximum",
  "segments": [
    {
      "original": "original text segment",
      "planned_tags": ["tag1", "tag2"],
      "tag_position": "before|after|mid",
      "punctuation_changes": "CAPS words, add ellipses, etc",
      "reasoning": "why these choices"
    }
  ],
  "non_verbal_placements": [
    {
      "after_segment": "text after which to place",
      "sound": "sighs|gulps|etc",
      "reasoning": "why here"
    }
  ]
}

